			"updated_at": "2026-05-06T16:07:09Z",
			"body": "> I think this applies to mobile as well, not just desktop?\r\n\r\nThe `convertNoteToMarkdown` function isn't exposed in the UI on mobile (see https://github.com/laurent22/joplin/pull/13841). If I recall correctly, there are also issues related to running `turndown` in the React Native main process that may cause `convertNoteToMarkdown` to not work if called by a plugin.",
